<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>设备已连接 - ArmorAuth</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/armorauth-ui.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="page-shell">
    <main class="center-stack">
        <section class="surface-card">
            <div class="surface-inner">
                <div class="toolbar">
                    <div class="brand-chip">
                        <span class="brand-mark">A</span>
                        <span class="brand-copy">
                            <strong>ArmorAuth</strong>
                            <span>设备已连接</span>
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="top-actions">
                        <button class="theme-toggle" type="button" data-theme-toggle>
                            <span class="theme-toggle-icon" data-theme-icon>☼</span>
                            <span data-theme-text>浅色</span>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="section-title">
                    <span class="eyebrow">已完成</span>
                    <h1>设备已连接</h1>
                    <p>现在可以返回设备继续操作。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="notice success">
                    如果设备没有自动刷新，请返回设备后重试。
                </div>
                <div class="info-grid">
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <strong>已完成确认</strong>
                        <p>本次激活已经生效，无需重复提交。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <strong>设备继续登录</strong>
                        <p>设备获取结果后会继续完成登录。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <strong>需要手动刷新时</strong>
                        <p>返回设备页面重新进入即可。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="action-row">
                    <a class="button primary" href="/">返回首页</a>
                    <a class="button secondary" href="/login">返回登录页</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</div>
<script src="/assets/armorauth-ui.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
